@page "/booking"

<PageTitle>Book Your Trip</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5 text-center">
    <!-- Section Headline -->
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #f8b500;">Gotorz</h2>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4">Book Your Trip with Gotorz</h4>

    <!-- White Content Box -->
    <div class="mx-auto p-4 text-start"
         style="
             background-color: white;
             border-radius: 5px;
             border: 1px solid lightgrey;
             box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
             max-width: 1000px;
             line-height: 1.8;
         ">

        <p>
            At Gotorz, we’re all about creating exciting travel experiences to new destinations — short and sweet, or long and adventurous.
            The more unique, the better!
        </p>

        <p>
            Our website is designed to make planning and booking your trip easy. From finding the right flight to selecting travel dates and preferences — we’ve made it super simple.
        </p>

        <p>
            Not sure which flight to choose? No problem! Just select the destination and travel month — the system will show you all available offers, sorted by the best deals.
        </p>

        <p>
            Prices are dynamic based on the number of travelers, so once you input the group size, the system will calculate the full price for you.
        </p>

        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">Like a trip you see? You’ve got two booking options:</h5>

        <ol>
            <li><strong>Book it yourself:</strong> Log in and go through the website — the process is super easy and doesn't require any special skills.</li>
            <li><strong>Use our chat support:</strong> You can message us on the site or through our social channels. Our team will help fill in your info and complete the booking for you.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>
            Once your booking is confirmed, we’ll send you a confirmation message. Our team will then assign your tickets and send everything to you via email or WhatsApp within a few hours.
        </p>

        <p><em>There’s nothing for you to worry about — we’ve got you covered.</em></p>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <!-- Steps -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold">Step-by-Step Booking Instructions:</h5>
        <ol>
            <li>Pick the travel offer that suits you (choose departure airport, destination, and dates).</li>
            <li>Enter the number of travelers to calculate total price.</li>
            <li>Click on the offer you like most.</li>
            <li>Log in or create an account using your email.</li>
            <li>Enter full names of all travelers (as shown in passports).</li>
            <li>Pick your preferred seats or extra services, if available.</li>
            <li>Request the invoice.</li>
            <li>Pay the invoice online or via direct bank transfer to our European account.</li>
            <li>Hotel vouchers and confirmations will be sent within 24 hours of payment.</li>
            <li>Airport transfer details (if booked) will be sent closer to your departure date.</li>
            <li>Our support team is available for questions at any time!</li>
        </ol>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <!-- Payment Methods -->
        <h5 class="fw-bold">Accepted Payment Methods:</h5>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Credit/Debit Card:</strong> Visa, Mastercard, or any card type accepted globally.</li>
            <li><strong>Bank Transfer:</strong> You can choose to pay via bank transfer to our official IBAN account. Payment instructions are provided at checkout or via customer support.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3">
            These options will appear at checkout or can be requested directly from our support team.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>